Narrative

On 4/27/23, the Maryland State Police Computer Crimes Section /Maryland Internet Crimes Against Children Task Force received NCMEC CyberTip # 159798628. The Cyber Tip, generated by Snapchat, indicated that a subject uploaded child pornography to the internet. The CyberTip was assigned to TFC Cooke for investigation.

 

The CyberTip provided the following information pertaining to the suspect:

 

Date of Birth: 06-27-1995
Email Address: no20056789@gmail.com
Screen/User Name: nono200550022
IP Address: 24.154.95.46     04-04-2023 01:41:01 UTC 

 

The CyberTip contained 19 reported child pornography files. TFC Cooke reviewed the reported child pornography files and determined that all 19 files constitute child pornography as it is defined under Maryland law. Three of these files are described below:

 

Filename: nono200550022-None-8689eeca-6416-5ef4-970b-dc70fc2bba5b~1-7cc2557cd5.jpg
Description: Color Image file showing a fully nude female, reasonably believed to be 3 - 5 years of age, being vaginally penetrated by an adult male's erect penis. The female is grossly underdeveloped, devoid of pubic hair, and significantly smaller than the adult male.
Upload Date/Time: 2023-04-04 T01:38:09.987Z

Filename: nono200550022-None-8689eeca-6416-5ef4-970b-dc70fc2bba5b~1-ee9c49ce1b.jpg
Description: color image file of a fully nude female, reasonably believed to be between 3 - 5 years of age, laying on her back and being vaginally penetrated by an adult male's erect penis. The female is grossly underdeveloped, devoid of pubic hair, and significantly smaller compared to the adult male.
Upload Date/Time: 2023-04-04 T01:38:09.987Z

Filename: nono200550022-None-8689eeca-6416-5ef4-970b-dc70fc2bba5b~1-a103944b37.jpg
Description: color image file of a female, reasonably believed to be between 4 - 6 years of age, performing fellatio on an adult male's erect penis. The female's face is underdeveloped and her hands are significantly smaller compared to the adult male body.
Upload Date/Time: 2023-04-04 T01:38:09.987Z

 

The CyberTip indicated that the following IP address 24.154.95.46 (04-04-2023 01:38:09 UTC) was utilized to upload the reported contraband files.

 

TFC Cooke conducted a query of the upload IP address through an open-source database and determined that it is registered through Armstrong Cable Services and geo-locates generally to the Rising Sun area of Cecil County, Maryland.
 

TFC Cooke transmitted investigative subpoena requests to the Howard County Office of the State’s Attorney for Armstrong Cable / Google subscriber information.
